Relationships:
- CUSTOMER 1:M ORDER (A customer can have many orders)
- ORDER 1:M ORDER_DETAIL (An order can have multiple products)
- PRODUCT 1:M ORDER_DETAIL (A product can appear in many orders)
- MANUFACTURER 1:M PRODUCT (A manufacturer makes many products)
- PRODUCT 1:1 INVENTORY (Each product has one inventory record)
- MANUFACTURER 1:M MANUFACTURER_ORDER (A manufacturer can receive many orders)
- MANUFACTURER_ORDER 1:M MANUFACTURER_ORDER_DETAIL (A manufacturer order can have multiple products)